Women impressed at this year&rsquo;s BAKE Awards. They scooped awards in eight categories. The awards were organised by the Bloggers Association of Kenya. At least 400 guests attended the dinner at Crowne Plaza. Creative writing blog Magunga.com was voted the best blog in the country. Some of those awarded included, potentash.com, wandianjoya.com, mummytales.com, healthkenya.com, lifeinmombasa.com, kaluhiskitchen.com, curveswithstyle.com and Safari254.com. Some 10,000 blogs were submitted to the judging panel for the 23 categories. The winners included first-timer owaahh.com, biznews.co.ke, healthkenya.co.ke and potentash.com.